
<div class="row col-xs-12">
    <h2>Choose a Program to Start Learning:</h2>
    <p>We offer a wide variety of tutorials. Please explore below and start learning today. We are constantly updating and adding new content. Always check our homepage for the latest news.</p>
</div>
<div class="row col-xs-12 col-sm-12 choose-program">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-2 img-wrapper">
        <img class="img-responsive" src="~/Content/Images/Microsoft-Excel-Mac-icon.png" />
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10 program">
        <h3>@Html.ActionLink("Microsoft Excel >", "MicrosoftExcel")</h3>
        <p class="program-text">One of our most popular courses to date. Start your new home budget or track your monthly bills with the ease of a few clicks. For all different levels of experience!</p>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row col-xs-12 col-sm-12 choose-program">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-2 img-wrapper">
        <img class="img-responsive" src="~/Content/Images/Microsoft-PowerPoint-Mac-icon.png" />
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10 program">
        <h3>@Html.ActionLink("Microsoft PowerPoint >", "AddingContent", "Home")</h3>
        <p class="program-text">PowerPoint can really give you the advantage when used properly! Make those boring presentations exciting and aesthetically pleasing. For all different levels of experience!</p>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row col-xs-12 col-sm-12 choose-program">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-2 img-wrapper">
        <img style="max-width: 125px;max-height:125px;"class="img-responsive" src="~/Content/Images/Microsoft-Word-Mac-icon.png" />
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10 program">
        <h3>@Html.ActionLink("Learn Microsoft Word >", "Maintenance", "Home")</h3>
        <p class="program-text">A powerful tool; Word has tons of hidden secrets that can help you perfect that essay you've been procrastinating to write! Word can also be used for other purposes besides writing! For all different levels of experience!</p>
    </div>
</div>